def count_carry_operations(A: int, B: int) -> int:
    carry = 1
    A = str(A)[::-1]
    B = str(B)[::-1]
    carry_count = 0
    for i in range(len(A)):
        a = int(A[i])
        b = int(B[i])
        summ = a + b + carry
        if summ > 9:
            carry = 1
            carry_count += 1
        else:
            carry = 0
    return carry_count
